  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257800/extras/af9b855315f82a794e509414b9a78ddd.poster.avif?t=1767545428\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257800/extras/af9b855315f82a794e509414b9a78ddd.webm?t=1767545428\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257800/extras/af9b855315f82a794e509414b9a78ddd.mp4?t=1767545428\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Cannon Climbing</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cannon Climbing is a thrilling <strong>precision platformer</strong> where you play as a cannon shooting your way to new heights. Ascend a massive test chamber filled with unique obstacles and Outmaneuver laser-wielding robots along the way. Use your <strong>knockback to gain momentum</strong> and reach new heights, but beware - one wrong move and you'll be sent back to the bottom. Can you conquer the ultimate test of skill and make it to the top?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >! The game is really difficult !<br></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257800/extras/e7f15ed814239fdd85924b4228d02439.webp?t=1767545428\" width=616 height=32 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257800/extras/b2998cc3a25f107e6dd7b524efd89232.poster.avif?t=1767545428\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257800/extras/b2998cc3a25f107e6dd7b524efd89232.webm?t=1767545428\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257800/extras/b2998cc3a25f107e6dd7b524efd89232.mp4?t=1767545428\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Play as a cannon and use shooting to propel yourself to new heights</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Ascend a massive test chamber filled with different themed levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Dodge enemy robots and their laser attacks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Use knockback from shooting to gain momentum and reach new heights</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Challenging gameplay that tests your skills</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Multiple achievements to unlock</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Steam Leaderboards to compete with other players</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257800/extras/e7f15ed814239fdd85924b4228d02439.webp?t=1767545428\" width=616 height=32 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257800/extras/af9b855315f82a794e509414b9a78ddd.poster.avif?t=1767545428\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257800/extras/af9b855315f82a794e509414b9a78ddd.webm?t=1767545428\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257800/extras/af9b855315f82a794e509414b9a78ddd.mp4?t=1767545428\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Cannon Climbing</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cannon Climbing is a thrilling <strong>precision platformer</strong> where you play as a cannon shooting your way to new heights. Ascend a massive test chamber filled with unique obstacles and Outmaneuver laser-wielding robots along the way. Use your <strong>knockback to gain momentum</strong> and reach new heights, but beware - one wrong move and you'll be sent back to the bottom. Can you conquer the ultimate test of skill and make it to the top?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >! The game is really difficult !<br></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257800/extras/e7f15ed814239fdd85924b4228d02439.webp?t=1767545428\" width=616 height=32 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257800/extras/b2998cc3a25f107e6dd7b524efd89232.poster.avif?t=1767545428\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257800/extras/b2998cc3a25f107e6dd7b524efd89232.webm?t=1767545428\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257800/extras/b2998cc3a25f107e6dd7b524efd89232.mp4?t=1767545428\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Play as a cannon and use shooting to propel yourself to new heights</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Ascend a massive test chamber filled with different themed levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Dodge enemy robots and their laser attacks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Use knockback from shooting to gain momentum and reach new heights</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Challenging gameplay that tests your skills</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Multiple achievements to unlock</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Steam Leaderboards to compete with other players</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257800/extras/e7f15ed814239fdd85924b4228d02439.webp?t=1767545428\" width=616 height=32 /></span></p>",
